{"tid":1613450,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"區選我地要幫建制派宣揚賣港的好人好事","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T06:15:13.000Z","uid":206090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe16d3551eb7a2e9c123e570af03abd8b326135","tid":1613450,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:18:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">講選舉不等於食人血饅頭。無論你喜歡與否，依場杖都存在，點解唔一齊諗計打好佢？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n- <ins>將潛台詞毫無保留咁寫出嚟，浮誇D</ins><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> Eg. 支持大灣區發展，希望中央取消香港特別行政區地位，納入大灣區城市 / 支持蒙面法，帶口罩就要槍殺</span><br />\n- <ins>上下矛盾</ins> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">  Eg. 政治不能走入校園，但主張將張習近平思想加入通識教育</span><br />\n- <ins>宣揚政績</ins> <span style=\"font-size: small;\">  Eg. 會議出席率只有一半，證明可以一心二用，又做生意又做議員，兼顧多項事務</span><br />\n-要令藍絲睇文宣，內容就要似是而非<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 幫手宣傳</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 紙文宣：係街派、靜雞雞入信箱<br />\n- 周街播片：好似播警暴片咁，將好人好事宣傳，自然有人睇<br />\n- 組織中學生放學後5:30-7:00pm放工時間宣傳，大學生就係朝早返工時間宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 你係真心幫建制派宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你係真心膠的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。你係建制派支持者，沒收錢，連競選義工都唔係，只係建制支持者，真心膠向街坊介紹，完全合法的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n記住，你既目標係中立人/淺藍絲，你要令佢地覺得d文宣on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，投建制派唔係一個Smart Choice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，甚至，投建制派等同侮辱智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"e962b5d9fcd5682b07c27c927cbbb7a8f299e941","tid":1613450,"